7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Descript and Steve AI share a solid foundation of core features including Auto Captions, Templates, Voice Over. Where Descript pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Screen Recording, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on this capability. On the other hand, Steve AI uniquely offers Text To Video and Stock Footage, giving it an edge for users who prioritize these areas. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Descript holds an overall score of 8/10 and an ease of use score of 8/10, while Steve AI scores 6/10 overall and 8/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Steve AI comes in at a lower starting price of $20/mo, while Descript begins at $24/mo. Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. Descript's free tier and Steve AI's free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
